# Thread subjected:  Happy New Year's Eve-Eve
# T19,C6/10 (D>P) sent Sun Jan 7 2018, 1221 Gtime / 1121 Ptime
# ∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙·∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙·∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙·∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙·∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙∙·∙∙
